{
  "message": "test: expand fuzz corpus for osc_marker, recorder_event, fts_query\n\n- osc_marker_parser: 5 new seeds (full A\u2192B\u2192C\u2192D lifecycle, two\n  back-to-back commands with nonzero exit, ANSI-colored markers,\n  malformed/partial markers, long output between C and D)\n- recorder_event_json: 5 new seeds (ingress_text, egress_output,\n  control_marker, wrong schema version, extra unknown fields)\n- fts_query: 5 new seeds (column filter, prefix, NEAR, boolean\n  OR/AND/NOT, SQL injection attempt via parameterized query)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
